                    <p>How do we value cost savings? What are the real benefits of outsourcing? What are the business values?</p>
                    <p>When we started our company, these are the questions that we ask ourselves. What will be our benefits? Are we going to bring any business value? What are our intentions? Can we sell it? What are our advantages?</p>
                    <p>The number 1 reason why businesses turn to outsourcing is to CUT COSTS and who doesn’t want to save money?</p>


                </div>
                <!-- End About text -->
                <!-- Img -->
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-7 col-md-pull-5 col-lg-pull-6 col-lg-6">
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="~/images/estimates.JPG" class="rounded float-right" alt="...">
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br />
            <div class="row wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 ">
                    <h4>Let’s start by evaluating how much your single regular employee costs you:</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Salary $30,000 – $40,000 a year to perform clerical duties. This role is usually attributed to a admin assistant.</li>
                        <li>Insurance $600 - $700 a year to for the employee's insurance </li>
                        <li>Leaves and Benefits $3,168</li>
                        <li>Bonus $1000</li>
                        <li>Kiwisaver $1,123.20</li>
                        <li>Other associated costs are: Payroll taxes 10%, and benefits around 15%.</li>

                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 ">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Software Licenses - $119</li>
                        <li>Desktop / Laptop - $600 </li>
                        <li>PC Hardware $200</li>
                        <li>Phone $100</li>
                        <li>Headset $50</li>
                        <li>Desk $300</li>
                        <li>Cabling $200</li>
                        <li>Other technology associated costs around 15%.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 ">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Rent</li>
                        <li>Utilities </li>
                        <li>Internet Access</li>
                        <li>Office Supplies</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 ">
                    <br />
                    <ul>
                        <li>Training - $5,000</li>
                        <li>Attrition (Retraining) - $5,000 </li>
                        <li>Recruitment $1500</li>
                        <li>Support $200</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <div class="row wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <h2>In total we have estimated that a company spends roughly around $56,800 a year on a single employee</h2>
                    <p>These are combinations of fix and variable costs. Budgeting will be easy as our service will be fixed in price. Not only that you will be paying a fixed price, the service is flexible as well. We can tailor fit it to the skills you are requiring. </p>
                    <p>The agents are not limited to the tasks at-hand, we can hire and train someone with the particular expertise you feel the necessity for. Rest assured that their main role is still their priority</p>
                    <p>Everything is monitored by our leaders and quality management team, giving you peace of mind and will be notified of any issues with regards to the effect on performance.</p>
                </div>

            </div>
            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <div class="row wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6">
                    <h3>When you avail our non-voiced services you will be saving $31,840 annually</h3>
                    <p>While saving $15,200 on our voiced campaigns</p>
                    <p>Non-voiced campaigns can do the non-essential tasks for you while offerring office support and can receive and answers email enquiries. </p>
                    <p>Voiced campaigns simply have the ability to answer and make phone calls while also can be trained to do the non-essential tasks for you on downtime or when you require them </p>
                    <p>This is what we meant by our services can be tailor-fitted, it all depends on your requirements as you have the ability to take advantage of our agents skillsets, rest assured that it will be done in a professional manner and great quality.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 ">
                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="~/images/savings.JPG" class="rounded float-left" alt="...">
                    </div>
