            </div>

            <br />
            <br />
            <br />
            <div class="row wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.2s">
                <div class="col-xs-12">
                    <h4>Final Thoughts</h4>
                    <p>I'm a 14years IT Practitioner and in my industry outsourcing is very common and a proven cost effective method. Why pay a developer in NZ $80,000 -$140,000 a year when they can get someone in the offshore for $40,000 or less. With a single salary budget in NZ rate you can hire 2 or 3 more overseas.</p>
                    <p>Take advantage of our 1 week free trial and test our skills and capabilities. </p>
